---
---
<section id="target-market" class="py-24 bg-white overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-16" data-aos="fade-up">
            <span class="text-brand-600 font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-sm bg-brand-50 px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-brand-100">Siapa Kami Bantu?</span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-4">Solusi Tepat untuk Usaha Anda</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-500 mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Dirancang khusus untuk memenuhi kebutuhan operasional bisnis menengah ke bawah agar lebih profesional dan terorganisir.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <!-- Market 1: Sembako -->
            <div data-aos="fade-right" class="group relative p-8 rounded-3xl bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 hover:bg-brand-600 hover:border-brand-500 transition-all duration-500">
                <div class="relative z-10">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-brand-600 mb-6 shadow-sm group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:bg-brand-500 group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300">
                        <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M16 11V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4M5 9h14l1 12H4L5 9z"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">Toko Sembako (Grosir & Ritel)</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 group-hover:text-brand-100 transition-colors leading-relaxed">Kelola ribuan item stok dengan mudah. Pantau harga modal dan jual secara otomatis. Stock opname ribuan item kini bisa selesai dalam hitungan menit.</p>
                    <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3">
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
                            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-500 group-hover:text-brand-300" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
                            <span>Support Scan Barcode</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
                            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-500 group-hover:text-brand-300" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
                            <span>Harga Bertingkat (Grosir/Ritel)</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <!-- Decorative Icon Background -->
                <div class="absolute bottom-4 right-4 opacity-5 group-hover:opacity-10 transition-opacity">
                     <svg class="w-32 h-32" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M16 11V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4M5 9h14l1 12H4L5 9z"></path></svg>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Market 2: F&B UMKM -->
            <div data-aos="fade-left" class="group relative p-8 rounded-3xl bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 hover:bg-purple-600 hover:border-purple-500 transition-all duration-500">
                <div class="relative z-10">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-purple-600 mb-6 shadow-sm group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:bg-purple-500 group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300">
                        <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">F&B (Kafe, Resto, Kedai)</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 group-hover:text-purple-100 transition-colors leading-relaxed">Kelola resep bahan baku (COGS) dengan detail. Stok bahan otomatis berkurang setiap ada pesanan. Minimalisir kebocoran stok di dapur.</p>
                    <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3">
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
                            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-purple-500 group-hover:text-purple-300" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
                            <span>Manajemen Resep & Bahan</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
                            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-purple-500 group-hover:text-purple-300" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
                            <span>Multi-Varian Produk</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <!-- Decorative Icon Background -->
                <div class="absolute bottom-4 right-4 opacity-5 group-hover:opacity-10 transition-opacity">
                    <svg class="w-32 h-32" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"></path></svg>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Call to Action for specific needs -->
        <div data-aos="fade-up" class="mt-16 p-8 rounded-3xl bg-slate-900 text-center relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="relative z-10">
                <h4 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Bisnis Anda berbeda dari kategori di atas?</h4>
                <p class="text-slate-400 mb-8 max-w-xl mx-auto">Tenang, sistem Jaripos sangat fleksibel untuk berbagai jenis usaha dagang lainnya. Konsultasikan kebutuhan Anda dengan tim kami.</p>
                <a href="https://wa.me/6281234567890" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 bg-brand-500 text-white font-bold rounded-full hover:bg-brand-600 transition shadow-lg shadow-brand-500/20">
                    <i class="fab fa-whatsapp text-lg"></i>
                    Konsultasi Gratis
                </a>
            </div>
            <!-- Abstract background shape -->
            <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-brand-500/10 blur-3xl -mr-32 -mt-32"></div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-64 h-64 bg-purple-500/10 blur-3xl -ml-32 -mb-32"></div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
